Facebook Marketplace Scraper

This is a simple scraper for Facebook Marketplace. It uses Playwright to scrape the data and save it to a CSV / JSON /

Example usage:

{
  "startUrls": [
    { "url": "https://www.facebook.com/marketplace/telaviv/apartments-for-rent" }
  ],
  "proxy": { "useApifyProxy": true }
}

